---
title: Thai Pork Loin Stir-fry with green beans and coriander
description: This Thai-inspired pork stir-fry is our take on a classic Pad Krapow Moo. The tender green beans add some welcome vibrancy while the chilli and ginger provide a bit of bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R02_W16_IE_IEXCP0147-3_Main_high-e9897683.jpg
